959
00:57:16,012 --> 00:57:16,979
The bullet.

960
00:57:17,013 --> 00:57:22,550
♪ ♪

961
00:57:22,585 --> 00:57:24,587
(car engine starting)

962
00:57:24,620 --> 00:57:32,895
♪ ♪

